	(text_box "NOTE:\nTVS on servo power input (D5) is set for a 5VDC working voltage.\n\nIf you use a higher voltage servo (e.g., 6V or 12V), the TVS diode MUST be replaced with an appropriate value, or removed entirely.\n\nWARNING:\nVSERVO is tied to V5 by default by +5V; if you use a different VSERVO voltage, delete JP5 or make it open by default."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
